oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Shelter Of Your Eyes - Bobby And Jeannie Bare performance - 1976-09
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of The Shelter Of Your Eyes, written by Don Williams, produced by Bobby Bare and Bill Rice, recorded in September 1976 at RCA Victor Studio in Nashville, Tenn., and performed by Bobby Bare and Jeannie Bare. Most likely commercial recording (RCA Victor PB-10852).
